svg.text: A furniture store is having a big sale. Compare the original prices and the sale prices. Then,
in pairs, figure out what discount the store is offering on each item, e.g.:
Zhè zhāng chuáng dǎ jǐ zhé?
Zhè zhāng chuáng dǎ bā zhé.
Ms. Wang has just started dating Mr. Li. She wants to be nice and asks Mr. Li what he would
like to do, where he would like to go, etc. Mr. Li also wants to be nice, so he leaves it up to Ms.
Wang to decide. In pairs, role-play and see if you and your partner can settle on a day, time,
你想去哪儿玩儿，我们就去哪儿玩儿。
Nǐ xiǎng qù nǎr wánr, wǒmen jiù qù nǎr wánr.
Find out what he would like to do.
Find out what cuisine he prefers.
Find out when he would like to see a movie.
Find out which city he would like to travel to.
